//*  |                                                              |
//*   --------------------------------------------------------------
//*
//* ----HISTORY: FOR MON1 SYSRES MOVE TO 3390, NEW VOLSER=S$RES1
//*         RAN: 04/03/98 ...... DUMP STEP
//*            : 04/03/98 ...... VARY, DEL NOS, RESTORE
